{"tid":919658,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"這對情侶專找雙性戀女　共享同性異性3P做愛","createTime":"2018-11-28T08:15:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-28T08:42:46.000Z","uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"93ff32aa99347e13f6687916f1abb8a64f334522","tid":919658,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T08:15:03.000Z","msg":"美國紐約一名36歲男子拉姆(Elan Ram)和26歲女友荷頓(Kat Horton)有一個特殊的嗜好，那就是他們專找雙性戀女約砲，同時共享同性、異性的3P做愛，絕頂升天。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《太陽報》報導，拉姆和荷頓喜歡「開放式關係」，拉姆更強調，他不喜歡欺騙下的愛情，因此很能享受這種開放式關係所帶來的「誠實透明」，更認為這是一種健康的生活態度。而拉姆和荷頓，會在酒吧或透過APP約砲，專找雙性戀女性，一起享受3P做愛之樂，無論是男女與女女，3人都能在床上翻雲覆雨。<br />\n<br />\n荷頓也說，她喜歡的愛情模式，是以男性為中心，她也說這樣的3P模式讓她「超有安全感與滿足感」，她也強調：「我們的關係非常堅定，當然我們的『女朋友』也讓這段關係更穩固，我們也尊重彼此的界線。」<br />\n<br />\n拉姆還有個10歲兒子，但他說兒子很能接受他的性愛生活模式。他也說，有很多朋友的女友和老婆鄙視他，但也有些女性贊同他的做法，而他會好好珍惜這些女性朋友。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181128/640_c80eaa512ce5c91bd7b72e0c929ede29.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181128%2F640_c80eaa512ce5c91bd7b72e0c929ede29.jpg&h=f982e879&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181128/640_624d3f42c653c7394288e8776b8ef355.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181128%2F640_624d3f42c653c7394288e8776b8ef355.jpg&h=2dc965dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181128/640_a604fbc6cbdba5bca3340bce9d273469.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181128%2F640_a604fbc6cbdba5bca3340bce9d273469.jpg&h=759e3db5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181128/640_47166bafc25063e8b114cf90ad80e6f4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181128%2F640_47166bafc25063e8b114cf90ad80e6f4.jpg&h=05cd2174&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b1c529f7f3fe876c0eb90aca3a83052e62d6cf7d","tid":919658,"uid":31,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T08:25:39.000Z","msg":"人生贏家<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1a6e8295d3a401d81072467007168f2ba6565ac","tid":919658,"uid":184433,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T08:25:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"38a767be3953977054c6227b1236f0db5878c1a2","tid":919658,"uid":28770,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T08:26:47.000Z","msg":"情迷巴塞隆拿<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8acc14a797e7d4a68b76c156ab828c24b2d4da9","tid":919658,"uid":62409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T08:29:00.000Z","msg":"諗起溫打烏文作者"},{"pid":"3a8a577586076ff229c1d0aa0c2c9ae99c942c93","tid":919658,"uid":73443,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T08:40:36.000Z","msg":"右面條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c59f0094c7a5110b3274cbc6ec48286e2cb2ad58","tid":919658,"uid":164090,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T08:42:43.000Z","msg":"點解佢唔搵雙性戀既男性3p<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c53e26b67064b96500f5d37ff22e863e7d2635e6","tid":919658,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-28T08:42:46.000Z","msg":"正"}]}